data.description: You can smile now :) **Assumable FHA Mortgage Available at 3.5% (call for details)! **2023 ROOF Scheduled prior to closing! Welcome to 3127 SW Natura Ave, a charming 3 bed, 2 bathroom gem that's been totally renovated, allowing you to enjoy modern amenities while staying close to the beach!This property is located in a 55+ community just 5 minutes away from the beach. Whether you're looking for a peaceful getaway or an active lifestyle, you'll find it here! You'll also be right near some of the best restaurants, grocery stores, malls, and golf clubs in town. This house is perfect for anyone looking for an updated property close to all the action. It's a great place to call home. Home has hurricane shutters. Don't miss out on this amazing listing - schedule your showing today!
